    {
      "element_id": "sec-a-32",
      "element_type": "section",
      "paragraph_ref": "A-32",
      "title": "**A-32 Formed Heads**",
      "content": "Formed heads (ellipsoidal, torispherical, hemispherical, conical) are covered by this paragraph. For a 2:1 ellipsoidal head: \n\n```\nt=(P×D)/(2×S×E−0.2×P)\n```\n\nwhere D is the inside diameter. The joint efficiency E shall be taken from Table B-12 and the allowable stress S from Table M-1 per A-23. ",
      "page_number": 2,
      "parent_id": null,
      "cross_references": [
        {
          "source_id": "sec-a-32",
          "target_id": "tbl-b-12",
          "reference_text": "shall be taken from Table B-12",
